title: Bobby Texted Luke Bryan To See If He’s the Mystery Waffle House Tipper + We Build Our Apocalypse Survival Team + Morgan2 on what it would take to Reveal Her Boyfriend
itunes:title: Bobby Texted Luke Bryan To See If He’s the Mystery Waffle House Tipper + We Build Our Apocalypse Survival Team + Morgan2 on what it would take to Reveal Her Boyfriend
description:
Bobby tries to get to the bottom of who the mysterious Waffle House $1k tipper is so he texted Luke Bryan to see if it was him. We each pick 2 other members of the show who we would want on our team to survive an apocalypse. Morgan2 reveals why she hasn’t shared her boyfriend after vacation…and what it would take for her to do so.
